data.title: Some Descendants of the BARCELONA Family Related to George Washington 1st US President
data.text: 2. i. Ramon Berenquer I 'el viejo' DE BARCELONA Count of Barcelona [1035-1076] was born about 1023 in Barcelona, Catalonia, Spain and died 26 May 1076 in Barcelona, Catalonia, Spain about age 53. 3. i. Sybile DE BARCELONA 2 was born about 1035 in Barcelona, Catalonia, Spain 2 and died after 6 Jul 1074 of Bourgogne, France.2 Sybile married Henry I DE BURGUNDY,2 son of Robert 'the Old' 'Capet' DE BURGUNDY Duc de Bourgogne [1032-1076] and Helie DE SEMUR, about 1056.2 Henry was born about 1035 in Dijon, Cote d'Or, Bourgogne, France 2 and died 27 Jan 1074 of Bourgogne, France 2 about age 39. 4. i. Ramon Berenquer II DE BARCELONA 68 was born about 1053 in Prob Barcelona, Catalonia, Spain 68 and died 5 Dec 1082 in Killed on way to Gerona prob by twin brother Berenguer Ramon 68 about age 29. 5. i. Ramon Berenguer III 'el Grande' DE BARCELONA Conde de Barcelona 2 was born 11 Nov 1082 in Rodez, Spain 2 and died 19 Jul 1131 in Barcelona, Catalonia, Spain 2 at age 48. 7. ii. Ramon Berenquer IV 'el Sant' DE BARCELONA Marquis de Barcelona 2 was born about 1113 in Barcelona, Catalonia, Spain 2 and died 6 Aug 1162 in Borgo San Dalmazzo, Piedmont, Italy 2 about age 49. 8. i. Alfonso II 'the Chaste' DE ARAGON King of Aragon [1163-1196], Comte de Barcelona 2 was born about May 1152 in Barcelona, Catalonia, Spain,2 died 25 Apr 1196 in Avignon, Vaucluse, Provence, France 2 about age 43, and was buried in Notre Dame de Poblet, Spain.2
